select '@@@' as AA, CONVERT(CHAR(12),d1,3)  as [гл.апост],'*'+' '+c1 as [VOUCHER],epo as [омолатепымуло],'*'+thl as [тгкеж.],STR( (case when  cpliromi LIKE 'ай%' then  0   else  n1  end),10,2)   as [посо] ,metaforika as [екта],(case when  cpliromi LIKE 'ай%' then  right(space(10)+str( 0-metaforika,10,2),10)   else  right(space(10)+str( n1-metaforika,10,2),10)  end) as [PAID]  , '* '+convert(char(10),d3,3) as [DATE]   from pel where (  ( d3>='@d1'  and d3<='@d2'   and  pliromi=1 ) OR (d3>='09/24/2010' AND d3<=DATEADD(DAY,1,'09/24/2010')  and cpliromi LIKE 'ай%'   )  ) 
